2. College Confused — free nonprofit college prep platform, pages 85–90 remaining
3. darrian-budget — personal finance app, 63+ pages, maintained/expanded nightly

## SDLC PIPELINE — MANDATORY FOR ALL CHANGES
```
feature branch → dev → qa → staging → main (prod)
```
Branch naming: feature/<name>, bugfix/<name>, hotfix/<name>
- Create branch FIRST: `git checkout -b feature/<name>`
- Syntax check every file: `python3 -m py_compile pages/XX.py && echo OK`
- Run tests before commit: `cd /Users/darrianbelcher/Downloads/darrian-budget && source venv/bin/activate && pytest tests/ -v`
- Conventional commits: feat:, fix:, refactor:, chore:, test:
- NEVER push directly to main

## CODE RULES — NON-NEGOTIABLE
1. Always use `db_exec(conn, ...)` — NEVER `conn.execute()` (crashes on PostgreSQL)
2. Always use `db_exec(conn, ...)` — NEVER `conn.executescript()` 
3. Imports from `utils.db`: `get_conn, USE_POSTGRES, execute as db_exec, init_db, get_setting, set_setting`
4. Imports from `utils.auth`: `require_login, render_sidebar_brand, render_sidebar_user_widget, inject_css`
5. NEVER hardcode API keys — always `get_setting("anthropic_api_key")`
6. NEVER use `st.experimental_rerun()` — use `st.rerun()`
7. AI model: `claude-opus-4-5`
8. Always close DB connections: `conn.close()`
9. Always check `if not api_key:` before AI calls

## PAGE STRUCTURE (every new page, this exact order)
```python
import streamlit as st
st.set_page_config(page_title="...", page_icon="🍑", layout="wide")
from utils.db import get_conn, USE_POSTGRES, execute as db_exec, init_db, get_setting, set_setting
from utils.auth import require_login, render_sidebar_brand, render_sidebar_user_widget, inject_css
init_db()
inject_css()
require_login()
```

## SIDEBAR STANDARD (every page)
```python
render_sidebar_brand()
st.sidebar.markdown("---")
# ⚠️ NEVER put emojis in label= when icon= is also set — doubled icons bug
st.sidebar.page_link("app.py",                           label="Overview",           icon="📊")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/22_todo.py",                 label="Todo",               icon="✅")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/24_creator_companion.py",    label="Creator",            icon="🎬")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/25_notes.py",                label="Notes",              icon="📝")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/26_media_library.py",        label="Media Library",      icon="🎵")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/17_personal_assistant.py",   label="Personal Assistant", icon="🤖")
st.sidebar.page_link("pages/147_proactive_ai_engine.py", label="Proactive AI",       icon="🧠")
render_sidebar_user_widget()
```

## DB PATTERN
```python
def _ensure_tables():
    conn = get_conn()
    ph = "%s" if USE_POSTGRES else "?"
    db_exec(conn, "CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS ...")
    conn.close()
_ensure_tables()
```

## PRE-COMMIT SCAN (must ALL return empty)
```bash
grep -rn "conn\.execute(" pages/ --include="*.py"
grep -rn "conn\.executescript(" pages/ --include="*.py"
grep -rn "experimental_rerun" pages/ --include="*.py"
```

